Definition: any of several psychotic disorders characterized by distortions of reality and disturbances of thought and language and withdrawal from social contact
Synonyms: adj, all, insane, schizophrenic, pert, schizophrenic_disorder, schizophrenic_psychosis, dementia_praecox, psychosis, any, of, several, psychotic, disorders, characterized, by, distortions, reality, and, disturbances, thought, language, withdrawal, from, social, contact
Category: noun.state
